author: Econteachert205

posts.post_title: Sold Filling t205 needs for collectors
posts.post_content: Ive been breaking up my 05 set slowly, planning on keeping a few I really like and selling most of the rest.  To any 05 collectors out there who are set building, feel free to pm me.  I have a lot of commons in g/f/p in the 15-20 range, some raw sps in the same condition and some graded stuff as well.  Will be happy to email interested parties pics.
All replied to. Cards sold.  Thanks guys..
